  "title": "Business Development Executive (Packaging Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Identify and secure new clients in the areas of corrugated box packaging, offset packaging, and display stands</li><li>Expand the customer base by exploring and approaching potential packaging clients</li><li>Meet or exceed the sales goals established by the company</li><li>Initiate and support new projects with existing customers to drive continued business growth</li><li>Monitor and follow up on customer orders to ensure smooth processing and fulfillment</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Business, Sales or Marketing</li><li>Experience sales in packaging industry</li><li>Excellent communication, negotiation and presentation skills</li></ul><p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p><p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p><p><br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
